<html xmlns:o="urn:schemas-microsoft-com:office:office"
xmlns:w="urn:schemas-microsoft-com:office:word"
xmlns="http://www.w3.org/TR/REC-html40">
<head>
<meta charset="utf-8">
<style>
body { font-family: Calibri, sans-serif; margin: 40px; color: #222; }
h1 { font-size: 22pt; color: #1a1a2e; border-bottom: 2px solid #0f3460; padding-bottom: 8px; }
h2 { font-size: 14pt; color: #0f3460; margin-top: 24px; }
table { border-collapse: collapse; width: 100%; margin: 12px 0; }
th { background: #0f3460; color: white; text-align: left; padding: 8px 12px; font-size: 10pt; }
td { border: 1px solid #ddd; padding: 8px 12px; font-size: 10pt; }
tr:nth-child(even) { background: #f8f8f8; }
.status-done { color: #27ae60; font-weight: bold; }
.status-pending { color: #e67e22; font-weight: bold; }
p, li { font-size: 11pt; line-height: 1.6; }
.footer { margin-top: 40px; font-size: 9pt; color: #888; border-top: 1px solid #ddd; padding-top: 8px; }
</style>
</head>
<body>

<h1>Task Report - February 14, 2026</h1>
<p><strong>Project:</strong> PAGCOR Casino Reviews (pagcorcasino.ph)<br>
<strong>Stack:</strong> Next.js 14.1 + WordPress (Headless CMS via WPGraphQL)<br>
<strong>Server:</strong> AWS Lightsail (Ubuntu, aaPanel)</p>

<h2>Tasks Completed</h2>

<table>
<tr><th>#</th><th>Task</th><th>Status</th></tr>
<tr><td>1</td><td>Built Next.js frontend for production (standalone mode)</td><td class="status-done">Done</td></tr>
<tr><td>2</td><td>Installed Node.js v20.20.0 and PM2 on server</td><td class="status-done">Done</td></tr>
<tr><td>3</td><td>Uploaded standalone build files to server via SCP</td><td class="status-done">Done</td></tr>
<tr><td>4</td><td>Started Next.js app with PM2 on port 3000</td><td class="status-done">Done</td></tr>
<tr><td>5</td><td>Configured Nginx reverse proxy (Next.js + WordPress)</td><td class="status-done">Done</td></tr>
<tr><td>6</td><td>Fixed ISR/data refresh (added /etc/hosts entry to bypass Cloudflare)</td><td class="status-done">Done</td></tr>
<tr><td>7</td><td>Fixed WordPress home URL mismatch (http vs https)</td><td class="status-done">Done</td></tr>
<tr><td>8</td><td>Added HTTPS proxy detection to wp-config.php</td><td class="status-done">Done</td></tr>
<tr><td>9</td><td>Fixed Nginx config (FastCGI nesting issue causing wp-admin login failure)</td><td class="status-done">Done</td></tr>
<tr><td>10</td><td>Disabled FastCGI cache (was caching login cookies, causing redirect loop)</td><td class="status-done">Done</td></tr>
</table>

<h2>Current Architecture</h2>
<table>
<tr><th>Component</th><th>Location</th><th>Details</th></tr>
<tr><td>Next.js Frontend</td><td>/www/wwwroot/frontend</td><td>PM2 app "review-platform", port 3000</td></tr>
<tr><td>WordPress CMS</td><td>/www/wwwroot/pagcorcasino.ph</td><td>PHP 8.3, MySQL, WPGraphQL</td></tr>
<tr><td>Nginx</td><td>aaPanel managed</td><td>Reverse proxy: / → Next.js, /wp-admin /graphql → WordPress</td></tr>
</table>

<h2>Nginx Routing</h2>
<table>
<tr><th>Path</th><th>Destination</th></tr>
<tr><td>/ (default)</td><td>Next.js (port 3000)</td></tr>
<tr><td>/_next/static/</td><td>Next.js (cached 365d)</td></tr>
<tr><td>/wp-admin/</td><td>WordPress PHP</td></tr>
<tr><td>/wp-login.php</td><td>WordPress PHP</td></tr>
<tr><td>/wp-content/, /wp-includes/</td><td>WordPress static files</td></tr>
<tr><td>/graphql</td><td>WordPress PHP (WPGraphQL)</td></tr>
<tr><td>/wp-json/</td><td>WordPress REST API</td></tr>
<tr><td>*.php</td><td>WordPress PHP (FastCGI)</td></tr>
</table>

<h2>Pending / Follow-up Items</h2>
<table>
<tr><th>#</th><th>Item</th><th>Status</th></tr>
<tr><td>1</td><td>wp-admin login verified working</td><td class="status-done">Done</td></tr>
<tr><td>2</td><td>Set Featured Images for casino posts in WordPress</td><td class="status-pending">Pending</td></tr>
<tr><td>3</td><td>Replace placeholder affiliate URLs (example.com) with real URLs</td><td class="status-pending">Pending</td></tr>
<tr><td>4</td><td>Set up cms.pagcorcasino.ph subdomain (optional - for cleaner separation)</td><td class="status-pending">Optional</td></tr>
</table>

<h2>Key Files Modified</h2>
<ul>
<li><strong>next.config.mjs</strong> — Added <code>output: 'standalone'</code>, updated image config</li>
<li><strong>ecosystem.config.js</strong> — Created PM2 config for production</li>
<li><strong>/etc/hosts</strong> — Added <code>127.0.0.1 pagcorcasino.ph</code> for local API access</li>
<li><strong>wp-config.php</strong> — Added HTTPS proxy detection + FORCE_SSL_ADMIN</li>
<li><strong>Nginx pagcorcasino.ph.conf</strong> — Rewrote for dual Next.js + WordPress routing</li>
</ul>

